---
---
<section class="tw-mh">
  <div class="tw-mh-grid">
    <div class="tw-mh-copy">
      <div class="tw-mh-eyebrow">
        <span class="tw-mh-eyebrow-dot"></span>
        Tidewater Property Maintenance
      </div>
      <h1 class="tw-mh-title">Reliable. Professional. <em>Detail-driven.</em></h1>
      <p class="tw-mh-lede">In-house technicians and licensed contractors serving Tidewater-managed communities, rental owners, individual homeowners, and other associations across Maryland and Delaware.</p>
      <div class="tw-mh-actions">
        <a href="#contact" class="tw-btn tw-btn-primary tw-btn-lg">Request service</a>
        <a href="#services" class="tw-btn tw-btn-ghost">See what we handle &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <div class="tw-mh-meta">
        <div class="tw-mh-meta-cell"><span class="num">24/7</span><span class="lab">Emergency line</span></div>
        <div class="tw-mh-meta-cell"><span class="num">MD&nbsp;+&nbsp;DE</span><span class="lab">Service area</span></div>
        <div class="tw-mh-meta-cell"><span class="num">In-house</span><span class="lab">Vendor compliance</span></div>
        <div class="tw-mh-meta-cell"><span class="num">Price breaks</span><span class="lab">For managed properties</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tw-mh-side">
      <div class="tw-mh-card">
        <div class="tw-mh-card-head">
          <span class="id">WO #4421-MD &middot; Owings Mills</span>
          <span class="status">In progress</span>
        </div>
        <div class="tw-mh-card-body">
          <div class="tw-mh-card-pills">
            <span class="tw-mh-card-pill acc">Water mitigation</span>
            <span class="tw-mh-card-pill">Single-family rental</span>
            <span class="tw-mh-card-pill">Tidewater-managed</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="tw-mh-card-title">Pipe burst &mdash; basement standing water reported 6:42 AM</h3>
          <div class="tw-mh-timeline">
            <div class="tw-mh-tl-row">
              <span class="tw-mh-tl-time">6:42 AM</span>
              <div class="tw-mh-tl-dot"></div>
              <div class="tw-mh-tl-body"><strong>Emergency call received via 24/7 line</strong><span>Auto-categorized as emergency. On-call manager paged.</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="tw-mh-tl-row">
              <span class="tw-mh-tl-time">7:01 AM</span>
              <div class="tw-mh-tl-dot"></div>
              <div class="tw-mh-tl-body"><strong>Callback &amp; dispatch confirmed</strong><span>19-minute callback &mdash; under the 20-min standard.</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="tw-mh-tl-row">
              <span class="tw-mh-tl-time">8:14 AM</span>
              <div class="tw-mh-tl-dot"></div>
              <div class="tw-mh-tl-body"><strong>Tech on-site, water shut</strong><span>Two mitigation fans staged. Owner notified with photos.</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="tw-mh-tl-row muted">
              <span class="tw-mh-tl-time">Today</span>
              <div class="tw-mh-tl-dot"></div>
              <div class="tw-mh-tl-body"><strong>Insurance documentation prepared</strong><span>Claim packet routed to owner&rsquo;s adjuster.</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tw-mh-card-foot">
          <span>Tech: <strong>J. Ramirez</strong> &middot; Vendor compliance current</span>
          <span style="color:var(--tw-sage);font-weight:700;font-family:var(--tw-font-mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.08em;">LIVE</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
